There are two distinct sets of retainer springs.  One set (5 clips I 
think) is used to hold the sealed beam headlamp to its retaining ring 
(the grey piece) and the other set (7 clips?) is used to hold the chrome 
  outer trim piece to the retaining ring.

Bobs67bus(-at-)wmconnect.com wrote:
